A.8 fresh evidence browser-expression regression

RED
command: node scripts/check-worldos-objective-evidence-boundary.mjs
exit: 1
finding: evidence resource regex is not escaped for the browser expression
runtime reproduction: Chromium received /.(?:avif|webp|png|jpe?g|mp3|wav|ogg|m4a|css|js)(?:?|$)/i and rejected it.

ROOT CAUSE
inspectPage is serialized through a JavaScript template literal. resourceEntries used one escape layer while bitmapBytes and audioBytes used two, so Node consumed the backslashes before Runtime.evaluate.

